{
  "texts": [
    "The weight factor ℱ is assigned to summation values of semantic parameters γ, β, and λ.",
    "The Sim Hier (I x, I y) measure denotes the hierarchical- based similarity and is calculated using Formula 1, Sim attr I x, I y measure denotes the attribute-based similarity and is calculated using Formula 4 and Sim infer (I x, I y) measure denotes the inferred attribute-based similarity and is calculated using Formula 6.",
    "The fusion similarity of two instances ranges from 0 to 1, with higher similarity yielding values closer to 1.",
    "The Proposed Semantic-Based CF Recommendation ApproachIn this paper, we correspondingly proposed a new hybrid recommendation method called the \"Fusion-based Semantic CF\" approach.",
    "This approach combines traditional itembased collaborative filtering with fusion-based semantic similarity measures to enhance recommendation quality."
  ]
}